snippet.title: Astropulse: Reincarnation - Official Reveal Release (Extended Version)
snippet.description: Astropulse: Reincarnation, the new single-player, sci-fi third-person shooter/RPG set on a war-torn future Earth from Imagendary Studios and accomplished Blizzard artist Wei Wang.
